title: Governor Gretchen Whitmer: Michigan Protesters 'Endangering People's Lives'
description: Michigan Gov. Gretchen Whitmer lashed out at the protesters who surrounded the capitol on Wednesday, telling reporters they were "endangering people's lives."
content:
